channel.title: NEXIS 667 Runescape private server! great staff, needs players!
channel.description:
Great new server called NEXIS, currently has great staff and not as many players as there should be, as this is a pretty good server. Come along and see for yourself how good this is.
http://nexis-rsps.webs.com/webclient
it has; experienced coders, mature and reasonable staff great bossing and 100% all skills working (few summoning pouches still need to be added)
